        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The Commission establishes Docket Nos.MC2015–61 and CP2015-92 to consider the Request pertaining to the proposed Priority Mail Contract 128 product and the related contract, respectively.",
