        "id": "mineru_newspaper_baa51a22898f0d534a6c404ba8f12fb1_2_29",
        "observed_type": "list",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Federal Register Citation of Previous Announcement: [80 FR 38782, July 7, 20151 STATus: Closed Meeting. PLAcE: 100F Street NE., Washington, DC. DATE AND TIME OF PREVIOUSLY ANNOUNCED MEETinG: Thursday, July 9, 2015 at 2 p.m. CHANGE IN THE MEETinG: Time Change.",
        "bbox": [
          0.6494117647058824,
          0.4084848484848485,
          0.9262745098039216,
          0.5406060606060606
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_baa51a22898f0d534a6c404ba8f12fb1_2_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It is ordered: 1. The Commission establishes Docket Nos. MC2015-61and CP2015-92 to consider the matters raised in each docket. 2.Pursuant to 39 U.S.C. 505, Kenneth R. Moeller is appointed to serve as an officer of the Commission to represent the interests of the general public in these proceedings (Public Representative). 3. Comments are due no later than July 13, 2015. 4. The Secretary shall arrange for publication of this order in the Federal Register.",
        "bbox": [
          0.07137254901960784,
          0.4103030303030303,
          0.3466666666666667,
          0.6145454545454545
        ],
        "order": 19
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_baa51a22898f0d534a6c404ba8f12fb1_2_30",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The Closed Meeting scheduled for Thursday, July 9, 2015 at 2 p.m. has been changed to Thursday, July 9, 2015 at1 p.m.",
        "bbox": [
          0.6509803921568628,
          0.5412121212121213,
          0.9184313725490196,
          0.5896969696969697
        ],
        "order": 20
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_baa51a22898f0d534a6c404ba8f12fb1_2_31",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Af times, changes in Commission priorities require alterations in the scheduling of meeting items. For further information and to ascertain what, if any, matters have been added, deleted or postponed, please contact the Office of the Secretary at (202) 551–5400.",
        "bbox": [
          0.6509803921568628,
